strings: <voice_0x01001C96><se_high>media princess: See, this forest reminds me of something.
<voice_0x01001C97><se_high>media princess: Remember how we got out of the palace?
<voice_0x01001C98><se_high>media princess: I asked him several times to take me to Fabri, but in the end he gave up. Hide and take me out of the castle! revenge
<voice_0x01001C99><se_high>media princess: I miss everything, even dinner! But I got lost in the forest, and it was dark.
<voice_0x01001C9A><se_high>media princess: I remember crying because I was scared, but all of a sudden a maki came out of my pocket and I did it all at once!
<voice_0x01001C9C><se_high>media princess: Mansi is a special mouse...
